# Dependencies
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Lockfiles are deliberately COMMITTED, not ignored. They pin the exact
# dependency tree, which is what makes `npm ci` reproducible in CI and what
# stops a transitive update from silently breaking a build.

# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.test
.env.production
*.env

